Package org.example

Class Cell

java.lang.Object
org.example.Cell
Direct Known Subclasses:
FormulaCell, NumberCell, StringCell
public abstract class Cell extends Object
The Cell class represents a cell in a spreadsheet. It provides methods for managing dependencies, updating cell values, and handling circular dependencies.
